Package: WrightFisherSim
Type: Package
Title: Wright-Fisher Population Genetics Simulator with Mutations
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Youssef Ahmed", "Afify", email = "yafify@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hamza", "Ayman", role = "aut"),
    person("Hamsa", "Saber", role = "aut"),
    person("Salsabeel", "Mostafa", role = "aut")
    )
Description: A Wright-Fisher model simulator for population genetics that supports 
    genetic drift, bidirectional mutations, migration, population splits/merges, and 
    pulse events. Uses the Demes specification for demographic models. This R package
    provides a wrapper around the Python implementation using reticulate.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
